<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When using Zend_Uri, you can not use an url compliant with the RFC3986.</p>

<p>By default, Zend_Uri ask to Zend_Uri_Http to validate hostname which rely on Zend_Validate_Hostname.</p>

<p>In Zend_Uri_Http::validateHost(), Zend_Validate_Hostname is called with Zend_Validate_Hostname::ALLOW_ALL.</p>

<p>It should be possible to adjust this parameter to use Zend_Validate_Hostname::ALLOW_URI that allow to use an url compliant with the RFC3986.</p>

